Wendy's Names Brandon Solano Senior Vice President of Marketing

Jul 24, 2014, 08:00 ET
		  		  								
						 from   The Wendy's Company 











 
















































 

 






















































 























 

 

 
 
 
 







Brandon Solano, The Wendy's Company, Senior Vice President of Marketing (PRNewsFoto/The Wendy's Company) ¬†¬†¬†
									
